Module Assignment
Package stores

Class DataStore

java.lang.Object
stores.DataStore
public class DataStore extends Object
The DataStore class is responsible for storing and managing various types of data related to the application. Data range from student, staff objects, camp registration/withdrawal data, enquiry and suggestion data It provides methods to initialize, save, and retrieve data.
